For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at Londonâ€™s O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Museâ€™s most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, â€œthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the filmâ€™s alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.â€Fans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAXâ€™s cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAXÂ® Experience. For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at Londonâ€™s O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Museâ€™s most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, â€œthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the filmâ€™s alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.â€Fans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAXâ€™s cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAXÂ® Experience. In IMAX, MUSE fans will be immersed in a cinematic worldÂ  of unmatched scope and clarity, surrounded by next-generation precision audio that delivers pitch-perfect tuning and pin-point accuracy in custom-designed IMAX theatres.Theater safety measures will comply with governmental and exhibitor guidelines. Examples of typical measures taken may include but are not limited to use of masks by employees, social distancing and capacity constraints, as well as increased sanitation efforts. Please contact your local exhibitor for more information on their specific precautions.Available for pre order on the same day will be 2 different limited edition deluxe box sets which will be available via muse.mu and physical retail. description: SIMULATION THEORY FILMExperience on IMAX on 17 August: https://www.imax.com/museDigital download available 21 August: http://muse.mu/filmDeluxe box sets out 11 December. Pre-order now!From February to October of 2019 MUSE took their Simulation Theory Tour to over 28 countries and played in front of more than 1 MILLION people.Â  Now fans will be able to experience the spectacle and more,Â  beginning August 17th when â€œMUSE - Simulation Theory: The IMAX Experienceâ€ will be available exclusively in select IMAX Theaters around the world andÂ  August 21st when the Simulation Theory movie will be available for rent or download on iTunes, Amazon and Google Play (distribution will be via Eagle Rock Entertainment). For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at Londonâ€™s O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Museâ€™s most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, â€œthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the filmâ€™s alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.â€Fans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAXâ€™s cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAXÂ® Experience. In IMAX, MUSE fans will be immersed in a cinematic worldÂ  of unmatched scope and clarity, surrounded by next-generation precision audio that delivers pitch-perfect tuning and pin-point accuracy in custom-designed IMAX theatres.Theater safety measures will comply with governmental and exhibitor guidelines. Examples of typical measures taken may include but are not limited to use of masks by employees, social distancing and capacity constraints, as well as increased sanitation efforts. Please contact your local exhibitor for more information on their specific precautions.Available for pre order on the same day will be 2 different limited edition deluxe box sets which will be available via muse.mu and physical retail. To celebrate the release of the Deluxe box sets, MUSE also teamed up with Marvel Comics to create and release a custom Simulation Theory comic book and limited-edition poster.

title: UFC 252 Highlights | Miocic retains heavyweight title with decisive win over Cormier | CBS Sports HQ
tags: CBS|CBS Sports|sports|cbs sports hq|sports hq|hq
description: The third fight in classic fight trilogies doesn't always live up to the lofty expectations set by the two previous meetings. In the case of UFC heavyweight champion Stipe Miocic's rubber match with Daniel Cormier at UFC 252, however, the third meeting surpassed anything that happened in the first two bouts as Miocic managed to outwork Cormier over five rounds for a unanimous decision victory in a thrilling battle.The hype train of rising bantamweight Sugar Sean O'Malley took a detour on its trip toward crossover stardom after an apparent leg injury led to an opportunistic finish from Marlon Chito Vera on Saturday.The first round and a half of the UFC 252 heavyweight clash between Jairzinho Rozenstruik and Junior dos Santos belonged to dos Santos, but Rozenstruik proved once again that it only takes one of his shots to turn a fight, scoring a TKO in the second round to rebound from a devastating loss in his last outing.SUBSCRIBE TO OUR CHANNEL:https://www.youtube.com/user/CBSSportsHQ FOLLOW US ON:Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/CBSSports/Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/cbssports/Twitter - https://twitter.com/CBSSports#UFC252 #Miocic #Cormier #UFC #MMA #SugarSeanOMalley #ChitoVera #Rozenstruik #JuniorDosSantos
